Uses of Class
sbmlme.converter.MEJsonReactionTypeAttributes

  • Packages that use MEJsonReactionTypeAttributes 
    Package Description
    sbmlme.converter
    The SBMLme converter package contains methods for a bidirectional converter between the JSON schema of a COBRAme model and its SBMLme representation.

      All reactions that create generic components.

      All reactions that transcribe a gene.
